{"tid":1462903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好衰俾人睇！","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:42:07.000Z","uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af1209efad0cc234b3ef394d6065b1fc4954c0b5","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"大家要記得今次係機場最大嘅敵人唔係黑警<br />\n而係自己<br />\n平時有去起防線守 轉場 都有黑警係到對持緊你可以點防守點攻擊都可以 因為你有黑警可以做事件中的 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中和劑</span></span> 你做到幾過火都好    <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警會自動補上柒事掩蓋</span></span><br />\n但係機場係冇黑警係到<br />\n所以大家要 留一線<br />\n因為你綁架住你旅客係到都冇用ga<br />\n我地癱瘓到50%已經好犀利夜晚多d人達到90%都可以<br />\n<br />\n人少有人少嘅做法<br />\n人多你點玩都得<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得初衷 <br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: blue;\">be water</span> 啊記住<br />\n<br />\nsorry199999999"},{"pid":"f607163c80c18f89201202149dd33b3467ad9e72","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3a29eb8dd69797815e0bef6c1ee2da8358396509","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a795777e658f2183e2111f0109805a31113706bb","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:28.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"607a56cc080e0d37f170754643c90f5d2046f6b3","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"324e571b708650c57b3221cde7a9e8fac8ea5598","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"459247f763145543d352fcf5d67bcc8deeeac863","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4966ac662ec6945ffe0a37b0e8117f79602be063","tid":1462903,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislik